content: Hello Jeyachandran! It's great to meet you. Thank you for accepting the invitation to this technical interview. Before we begin, I would like to review your resume and get an idea of your background and experiences. Can you tell me more about your project "AI Project Developer" at Shine Logics, where you developed a web app for mock interviews utilizing AI to ask voice-based questions based on uploaded resumes? What was your primary role in this project?
